# Marketing Dashboard Architecture: Executive Reporting Framework

## Overview

This document defines the comprehensive marketing dashboard architecture for executive reporting, visualization components, and real-time analytics for marketing teams persona.

**Document Level:** Level 3 - Technical Implementation  
**Target Audience:** Dashboard Developers, Marketing Data Scientists, Executive Reporting Teams  
**Technical Focus:** Real-time analytics with <10 second dashboard updates

